{
  "id": "adv_event_2301_01_03",
  "title": "先輩ボディーガード",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "妨害工作！？　まさか、そんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sabotage!? No way‚ something like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.6476417542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "残念ながら、そのまさかが起きてるみたいだ\nほら、これを見て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unfortunately‚ it seems like that's exactly what's happening.\nTake a look at this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8333333333,
      "endTime": 11.3833333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "これは……スプレー式の潤滑油じゃない\nドアの修理とかに使う物ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… a spray-type lubricant.\nIt's used for door repairs and such.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666667,
      "endTime": 17.4386848133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "あの男が僕とすれ違った時に落としていったんだ\n僕達のシューズの裏に塗るつもりだったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He dropped it when he passed by me.\nWasn't he planning to apply it to the soles of our shoes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6333333333,
      "endTime": 24.865260537399998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことされたら、滑って転んじゃいますよ\n怪我したらどうするんですか。悪質ですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If he does that‚ we might slip and fall.\nWhat if we get hurt? It's malicious~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "endTime": 32.789319865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……私達は練習の前に、シューズのチェックは\n必ずしてるから、こんなことしても無駄なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… We always check our shoes before practice‚\nso even if he does this‚ it won't work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33,
      "endTime": 40.5333331108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、プロなら道具の確認は当然だしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ as professionals‚ that's a given to check our equipment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7333333333,
      "endTime": 45.1331067403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "…………お、お二人の言う通りです！\nこころ達も舐められたものですよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Y-Yes‚ as both of you said!\nThey shouldn't underestimate us~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3333333333,
      "endTime": 53.332970746300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんみたいな卑怯な人、他にもいるんですね\n……私、がっかりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems there are people like Himeno-san who resort to such cowardly acts.\n…I'm disappointed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5333333333,
      "endTime": 61.144580682100006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "霧子と比べると、だいぶ残念な感じだけどね\nなんだか憎み切れないな、僕は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compared to Kiriko-san‚ this feels quite disappointing‚ but\nI can't completely hate him for some reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3333333333,
      "endTime": 69.1362587292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、どこの世界にもいい人もいれば悪い人もいる\n芸能界に限ったことじゃないわ、愛",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ in every world‚ there are both good and bad people.\nIt's not limited to the entertainment industry‚ Ai-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3333333333,
      "endTime": 76.4878231366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "お二人から大人の余裕を感じます。さすがです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can feel maturity from both of you. Well done…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "endTime": 80.7617006302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "で、これからどうします～？　訴訟もいいですし\nこれをネタにいろいろ要求してもいいですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what do we do now~? Filing a lawsuit would be an option‚ right~?\nWe could demand various things using this as leverage~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9666666667,
      "endTime": 88.097777621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "何もしないわ。放っておきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won't do anything. Let's just leave it be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3,
      "endTime": 90.8166666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。僕達はいつも通りパフォーマンスに集中しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ let's focus on our performance as usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0333333333,
      "endTime": 95.9029706319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "え～っ？　せっかくお仕置き出来る\nチャンスなのに～。残念ですぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh~? This was a chance to punish them~.\nIt's a shame!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1,
      "endTime": 101.8244446754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、それじゃこころが悪役みたいだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ KoKoro-chan would look like the villain‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0333333333,
      "endTime": 105.4333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "明日は本番よ。念のため、身の回りには\n十分に注意を払っておきなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow is the real deal. Just to be safe‚\nmake sure to pay attention to your surroundings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6333333333,
      "endTime": 111.48179143269999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12200.000000000004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳で、今日のミーティングはおしまい\n僕は自分の部屋に戻るよ。お休み",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ that's it for today's meeting.\nI'm going back to my room. Goodnight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6666666667,
      "endTime": 118.09918352759999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12700.000000000004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "お休みなさい、葵さん。……そろそろ私も失礼しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Goodnight‚ Aoi-san. I'll excuse myself soon too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3,
      "endTime": 124.04587278369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あの……莉央さん、本当にこのままでいいんですか？\n例えば、もし、莉央さんに万一何かあったら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Ria-san‚ are you sure it's okay to leave it like this?\nFor instance‚ if something were to happen to you suddenly――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0666666667,
      "endTime": 136.3228798549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.8
    },
